BP Iraq Head Townshend Replaces Tony Hayward on TNK-BP Board

-- B y   A n n a   S h i r y a e v s k a y a
-- 
2011-10-11T13:45:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/bp-iraq-head-townshend-replaces-tony-hayward-on-tnk-bp-board.html
BP appointed Michael Townshend, the
president of its Iraq operations, as a non-executive director on
the board of TNK-BP, its Russian oil venture with a group of
billionaires.  Townshend replaces former BP Chief Executive Officer  Tony
Hayward  on the board, BP said today in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anna Shiryaevskaya in Moscow at 
 ashiryaevska@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
